data.description: The Magnolia II-C features 1405 sq. ft. with 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths and a double car garage. Open concept family room, kitchen and dining room. Covered back porch. Home is located close to Fayetteville and Ft. Bragg. Just a short commute to Sanford or Lillington.
